or three-year problem.

29:14.066 --> 29:18.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Hence getting
the attention of U.S. officials
and officials in the reason.

29:20.566 --> 29:22.700 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Just final quick
question, Jeffrey Lewis.

29:22.700 --> 29:27.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
