they're doing this?

29:35.233 --> 29:38.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
®MD-BJEFFREY LEWIS:
Well, in the past,
they had a lot of help.

29:38.766 --> 29:42.866 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so we would see the
North Koreans poking around
in Russia and Ukraine
looking for technology.

29:42.866 --> 29:46.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think the reason this
