is because it really looks like

29:46.933 --> 29:49.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
something they
designed themselves.

29:49.000 --> 29:52.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So I think they have moved
from the point where they are
importing things and stealing

29:52.000 --> 29:53.866 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
information to actually
designing their own engines.

29:53.866 --> 29:55.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And that's a big step.

29:55.566 --> 29:58.566 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: It
certainly sounds like it.

29:58.566 --> 30:03.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Jeffrey Lewis with the Monterey
Institute of International
Studies, we thank you.

30:04.600 --> 30:09.600 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
®MD-BJEFFREY LEWIS: Thank you.

