region and returning to
their home countries.

30:39.533 --> 30:44.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This has had an impact across
the region, including in
Tunisia, a country that has sent

30:44.300 --> 30:47.800 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
