going to get a briefing this
week by the deputy attorney

50:06.166 --> 50:08.700 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
general, Rod Rosenstein.

50:08.700 --> 50:12.966 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But many of the reactions
to this, this latest
story are, well, we want
to know what's really

50:14.400 --> 50:16.466 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
