This NBC/Wall Street Journal
poll that came out this week,
I think came out yesterday,

50:49.666 --> 50:54.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
support, approval rating among
people who voted for Trump
87 percent, among Republicans

50:55.433 --> 50:57.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
