Hillary Clinton carried.

51:25.200 --> 51:26.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Only one, in fact, does.

51:26.966 --> 51:28.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
That's some of their
calculation, too.

51:28.566 --> 51:33.100 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The bottom hasn't dropped outs
